What an eye-opener...

289
00:26:21,133 --> 00:26:22,100
It's you.

290
00:26:22,633 --> 00:26:23,633
You are so tough.

291
00:26:25,300 --> 00:26:25,733
What?

292
00:26:27,500 --> 00:26:29,600
(Catfish)
You have made the catfish in the pond as a spiritual pet?

293
00:26:30,433 --> 00:26:31,700
You are so desperate

294
00:26:31,766 --> 00:26:32,900
to do such a stupid thing.

295
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:37,500
Catfishes could be cultivated into invincible whales before,

296
00:26:38,933 --> 00:26:40,566
but in the peak competition a year ago,

297
00:26:41,033 --> 00:26:43,100
the catfish of the Lingxiao Pavilion lost control

298
00:26:43,366 --> 00:26:44,833
and devoured its master

299
00:26:45,500 --> 00:26:47,133
and gained the vile name of master-killer.

300
00:26:48,733 --> 00:26:49,600
It wasn't true.

301
00:26:50,200 --> 00:26:51,300
It was an accident.

302
00:26:52,100 --> 00:26:53,733
An accident? Who do you think you are?

303
00:26:54,566 --> 00:26:56,000
The League issued the termination order.

304
00:26:56,700 --> 00:26:58,666
So the catfishes were wiped out.

305
00:26:59,533 --> 00:27:02,100
That one is kept here by my brother.

306
00:27:02,433 --> 00:27:04,066
It might be the only one on this continent.

307
00:27:04,666 --> 00:27:05,333
What's more,

308
00:27:06,133 --> 00:27:07,500
only the master of the Lingxiao Pavilion

309
00:27:07,566 --> 00:27:09,366
knows how to cultivate a catfish.

310
00:27:09,766 --> 00:27:11,133
It's a useless pet

311
00:27:11,300 --> 00:27:13,300
to others.

312
00:27:13,600 --> 00:27:14,533
Don't say that.

313
00:27:19,966 --> 00:27:21,333
So foolish and stubborn.

314
00:27:31,766 --> 00:27:32,566
Go, Nian.

315
00:27:42,333 --> 00:27:42,966
No.

316
00:27:47,100 --> 00:27:47,900
Devour it.

317
00:28:16,766 --> 00:28:17,766
Good job.

318
00:28:17,866 --> 00:28:18,433
Impressive.

319
00:28:23,900 --> 00:28:24,700
If you'll excuse me.

320
00:28:33,533 --> 00:28:35,300
The Bais are so persistent.

321
00:29:07,133 --> 00:29:08,033
Vine Sprite.

322
00:29:14,333 --> 00:29:15,833
Fly.

323
00:29:25,766 --> 00:29:27,133
I... I'm sorry.

324
00:29:27,333 --> 00:29:28,700
Please calm down.

325
00:29:29,233 --> 00:29:30,066
Miss Bai.

326
00:29:30,266 --> 00:29:32,366
We chased him for over ten li in three directions

327
00:29:32,566 --> 00:29:34,100
and still couldn't find Liu Fengmang.

328
00:29:34,500 --> 00:29:36,333
I... I guess he might

329
00:29:36,633 --> 00:29:38,933
have fallen from the cliff and died.

330
00:29:45,166 --> 00:29:47,166
You bunch of good-for-nothings!

331
00:29:47,666 --> 00:29:49,233
I was utterly disgraced by him.

332
00:29:49,533 --> 00:29:51,300
None of you is reliable.

333
00:29:52,733 --> 00:29:53,533
At all costs,

334
00:29:53,833 --> 00:29:55,700
bring him here, dead or alive.

335
00:30:06,466 --> 00:30:07,933
Tell me.

336
00:30:10,133 --> 00:30:12,233
Who do you want dead?

337
00:30:15,633 --> 00:30:16,333
Brother.

338
00:30:36,433 --> 00:30:37,966
What happened last night?

339
00:30:41,266 --> 00:30:42,166
It really

340
00:30:42,466 --> 00:30:43,366
wasn't a dream.

341
00:30:44,533 --> 00:30:45,600
That was what happened.

342
00:30:46,066 --> 00:30:47,700
That rascal humiliated me

343
00:30:48,133 --> 00:30:49,266
and used a catfish to...

344
00:30:49,766 --> 00:30:51,266
to devour Bai.

345
00:30:54,133 --> 00:30:56,933
Brother, you shall avenge me.

346
00:30:58,666 --> 00:30:59,766
How abhorrent!

347
00:31:00,233 --> 00:31:01,933
That is too much.

348
00:31:03,500 --> 00:31:06,833
He stole the discontinued catfish I managed to collect.

349
00:31:07,266 --> 00:31:09,500
Stupid brother, listen to my point!

350
00:31:10,833 --> 00:31:12,300
Isn't that catfish powerful?

351
00:31:12,933 --> 00:31:14,633
Why didn't you give it to me earlier?

352
00:31:15,233 --> 00:31:16,066
Powerful?

353
00:31:17,333 --> 00:31:18,233
No.

354
00:31:19,133 --> 00:31:21,366
A catfish has nothing special.

355
00:31:21,833 --> 00:31:23,733
Its only innate skill is devouring

356
00:31:23,966 --> 00:31:25,333
and can only be used

357
00:31:25,333 --> 00:31:27,366
on an unguarded and idling thing.

358
00:31:27,933 --> 00:31:29,433
You could've broken it

359
00:31:29,433 --> 00:31:31,333
if you had let your serpent resist a bit.

360
00:31:31,333 --> 00:31:32,966
I... I had done it.

361
00:31:33,366 --> 00:31:34,033
Anyway,

362
00:31:34,333 --> 00:31:35,733
it's confirmed

363
00:31:35,800 --> 00:31:37,300
that the catfish is useless.

364
00:31:37,533 --> 00:31:38,833
You are called a useless pet

365
00:31:39,233 --> 00:31:40,000
and an ominous beast.

366
00:31:40,266 --> 00:31:41,466
So your race is wiped out.

367
00:31:42,166 --> 00:31:43,466
It is not strong when it grows up.

368
00:31:43,833 --> 00:31:45,633
Not to mention it may devour its master.

369
00:31:46,433 --> 00:31:46,900
But

370
00:31:47,400 --> 00:31:48,833
there is an exception.

371
00:31:50,166 --> 00:31:51,700
Fan Lingxiao.

372
00:31:51,866 --> 00:31:52,666
Only I know

373
00:31:53,166 --> 00:31:54,266
how strong you are.

374
00:31:55,600 --> 00:31:57,033
But the man is dead.

375
00:31:57,733 --> 00:31:59,633
So nobody knows its secret.

376
00:31:59,933 --> 00:32:00,400
Because

377
00:32:01,700 --> 00:32:03,200
I know the secret of how you became strongest.

378
00:32:03,266 --> 00:32:05,666
That lecher is just a burden to us.

379
00:32:06,233 --> 00:32:07,733
He can do nothing.

380
00:32:08,166 --> 00:32:08,833
Nian.

381
00:32:09,500 --> 00:32:10,933
You must not be convinced by the reality

382
00:32:11,333 --> 00:32:12,500
and can't wait to prove yourself.

383
00:32:13,166 --> 00:32:14,966
We failed in the previous life.

384
00:32:15,833 --> 00:32:17,266
In this life, promise me

385
00:32:17,600 --> 00:32:18,666
that you will

386
00:32:19,133 --> 00:32:20,233
devour all obstacles.

387
00:32:20,300 --> 00:32:20,866
Trust me.

388
00:32:21,733 --> 00:32:23,466
I will handle him one day.

389
00:32:25,533 --> 00:32:26,133
Nian.

390
00:32:26,733 --> 00:32:27,666
As long as you are with me,

391
00:32:28,366 --> 00:32:29,666
I can retake all the things

392
00:32:29,966 --> 00:32:31,166
I have lost.

393
00:32:32,500 --> 00:32:32,833
Come.

394
00:32:38,600 --> 00:32:39,433
Join me

395
00:32:41,233 --> 00:32:42,600
to get to the peak.

